    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Technical and financial support for CPAP annual review and for CP-related activities, including capacity building related to programme implementation, monitoring and evaluation\r\n\r\n- Observe key international  as well as advocacy events (e.g. UN Day, World Population Day, State of the World Population Report, etc.).\r\n\r\n- Contribute to joint coordination/communication activities managed through the UNRC office as well as for UNDAF-related costs (e.g. UNDAF annual review, UNDAF outcome 3 activities, UNDAF M&E, etc.).\r\n\r\nSupport Government and NGO participants to meetings, workshops, international conferences etc."
      },
